```class Solution {
    public int minimumScore(String s, String t) {
        int n = s.length(), m = t.length();
        int res = m, left = 0, right = m - 1;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (i < m && s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(left)) left++;
            if (i < m && s.charAt(i) == t.charAt(right)) right--;
            if (left > right) res = Math.min(res, right - left + 1);
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
